node.text:
Would you try this recipe?

INGREDIENTS
500g beef mince
2 small carrots, finely diced
1 white onion, finely diced
2 cloves garlic, minced
2 tbsp oil
2 tsp salt
2 tsp pepper
1 tsp chili flakes
2 tbsp tomato paste
1/2 cup red wine
1 1/2 cups passata
1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
1 1/2 cups grated mozzarella
1/4 cup grated parmesan
8 par cooked flat lasagna noodles
Fresh basil
